## **3. YouTube Sentiment Analyzer**  
**`README.md`**

```markdown
# YouTube Sentiment Analyzer

This project analyzes sentiments from YouTube video comments using TextBlob. It visualizes the distribution of positive, negative, and neutral comments.

## Features
- Fetches top 100 comments from any YouTube video using the YouTube Data API
- Sentiment analysis using TextBlob
- Pie chart visualization of sentiment distribution

## Setup
1. Get a YouTube Data API key from [Google Cloud Console](https://console.developers.google.com).
2. Replace `YOUR_YOUTUBE_API_KEY` and `VIDEO_ID_HERE` in the script.

## Requirements
